- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses recent advances in named entity recognition and graph-based semi-supervised algorithms. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with extracting keyphrases from scientific articles. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still possible as the paper introduces a neural tagging model.
